					<br>
					<br>As you pass under the portcullis, you begin to realise the magnitude of the place.
					<br> Before it was shrouded by fog, but now the air has cleared and snow is falling;
					<br> you begin to feel how large the Castle really is.
					<br><br><br><br><br><br>
					
